To use, simply add the Nudge script to your HTML head:

  <script src="https://raw.github.com/chrisnolet/Nudge/master/js/nudge.js"></script>

Reload your page. You can now click on any element that has an #id.

To move elements, use the E, D, S and F keys.
To resize elements, use the I, K, J and L keys.

Use the Shift key to move and resize by 10 pixels at a time.



